1981;;Burned at the Stake;;American;;Bert I. Gordon;;Susan Swift, Albert Salmi, Guy Stockwell;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Burned_at_the_Stake;;In the Salem of 1692, a group of witches are burned at the stake. Now, in the 1980s, a witch comes back from the dead, possesses one of her descendants, and goes hunting for the occupants of the town to avenge her death.